            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Logy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ah, welcome Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You seem pretty busy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. But I just found a good place to take a break."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Lately, I've been getting a lot of requests to repair things like farm tools too, so I've gotten pretty busy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "It's fine as long as I can handle it myself, but... I might have to start getting picky about the work I accept."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I need to improve my skills so that I can finish my work faster..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You're pretty popular, Logy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Popular...? Well, I'm just glad that business is thriving..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Although I'd like to take a vacation..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Ahaha, what would you do if you had time?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Naturally, I would go traveling. Isn't that obvious?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "...It sounds like you're always either making weapons, or traveling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "That's all I need. I really enjoy this lifestyle."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
